name: Ll-compiler
body:
### LL-Compiler
LL Compiler is a small Little Lisp Language compiler. Developed by Danil Tumaykin and Igor Dultsev at Intel WS2012 at NGU-Intel Lab.

Further documentation is available at [LL-Compiler wiki at NSU-Intel Lab.](LL Compiler is a small Little Lisp Language compiler. Developed by Danil Tumaykin and Igor Dultsev at Intel WS2012 at NGU-Intel Lab.  Further documentation is available at http://www.i-lab.nsu.ru/wiki/index.php/LL_Compiler.)

### Support or Contact
Need some information or want to contact me: d.tumaykin@gmail.com.
